Fraser Kershaw https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fraser_Kershaw 0 Fraser Hart Kershaw Jr. is an activist in the clean water movement throughout the United States and Latin America. He made his television debut acting as multiple characters in the 2016 televised international feature film Behind the Water.
